theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 13
text = "Channel 2:
- The sound of wind, only in the upper frequencies of this channel.
- Chaotic beeping noises can be heard on this channel.
- Human radio communication should have a beep before but not after.

Channel 3:
- High pitched repetitive whirring sounds can be heard at the middle frequencies of this channel 
- The sound of wind can be heard at the low frequencies of this channel"

